sql:
SELECT DISTINCT f.parcelid as pid, f.userid, mlnumber, f.status, bd as county,
			f.address, lprice, marketvalue, activevalue, dom, unit, zip, ag.agent, offer, coffer, ndate, ntask, contract, pof, emd, realtorsadem as rademdums,
			f.msj, DATEDIFF(NOW(),lasthistorydate) as lasthistorydate, ((offer/lprice)*100) as offerpercent, f.type,
			s.status as statusalt, offerreceived,
			followdate, concat(x.name,' ',x.surname) as name_follow , f.userid_follow, f.pendes,
			(SELECT count(s.idfus) FROM xima.followup_schedule s WHERE s.userid=f.userid and s.parcelid=f.parcelid) as pt,
			(SELECT count(fa.agentid) FROM xima.follow_assignment fa WHERE fa.userid=f.userid and fa.parcelid=f.parcelid) as fa,
			(select	xima.followagent_type.`name` from xima.followagent_type where xima.followagent_type.idtype = ag.agenttype) as agenttype,
			if(ag.phone1 ='' ,if(ag.phone2 ='',if(ag.phone3 ='',if(ag.phone4='',ag.phone5,ag.phone4),ag.phone3),ag.phone2),ag.phone1) as phone1,

 IF(c.num_contract IS NULL, '0', c.num_contract) as contractn,
 			f.owner, f.financial, f.prior
			FROM xima.followup f
			INNER JOIN xima.followup_status s ON ((f.statusalt='N' AND f.status=s.code) OR f.statusalt=s.code)
			left join xima.ximausrs x on f.userid_follow=x.userid
			left JOIN xima.follow_assignment a ON (f.parcelid=a.parcelid AND f.userid=a.userid AND a.principal=1)
       LEFT JOIN xima.followagent ag ON (a.agentid=ag.agentid)
			LEFT JOIN (select f.userid, f.parcelid, count(*) as num_contract
    from xima.followup f
    inner join xima.follow_emails_assigment fea ON (f.parcelid = fea.parcelid and f.userid = fea.userid)
    inner join xima.follow_emails fe on (fea.idmail = fe.idmail)

    WHERE f.userid=7035  and fe.task=7 and f.type <>'DEL'
    group by f.userid, f.parcelid) as c ON (c.parcelid=f.parcelid AND c.userid=c.userid)
			WHERE f.userid =7035 AND type IN ('B','BM','S','L','P','LM','PM') ORDER BY followdate DESC, f.address ASC
